  {
    "id": "68e43a5e-9c66-4992-8293-82201bb6a2a2",
    "title": "LAST LAUGH: No. 1 Duke men's basketball rolls past No. 17 North Carolina 76-61",
    "date": "3/7/2026",
    "html": "<div class=\"sub-accordion\">\n  <button class=\"sub-accordion-btn\" onclick=\"toggleSubAccordion(this)\">\n    <span>杜克男篮主场完胜北卡夺得常规赛冠军<span class=\"tag tag-key\">2026.3.7</span></span>\n    <span class=\"sub-accordion-arrow\">&#9658;</span>\n  </button>\n  <div class=\"sub-accordion-body\">\n    <div class=\"cal-highlight\">\n      <strong>排名第一的杜克大学76-61击败排名第17的北卡大学</strong><br>\n      在常规赛最后一场比赛中，杜克男篮在主场Cameron Indoor Stadium完胜传统劲敌北卡，连续第二年保持主场全胜战绩。新生Cameron Boozer表现出色，贡献26分15篮板的两双数据。\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cal-item\">\n      <div class=\"cal-date\">球员表现</div>\n      <div><div class=\"cal-desc\">新生Cameron Boozer砍下26分15篮板，高年级球员Maliq Brown贡献赛季新高15分9篮板，在其最后一次主场比赛中表现卓越</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cal-item\">\n      <div class=\"cal-date\">赛季战绩</div>\n      <div><div class=\"cal-desc\">杜克以29胜2负、ACC联盟17胜1负的优异战绩结束常规赛，已锁定ACC锦标赛头号种子，将于周四晚7点在夏洛特开始季后赛征程</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cal-item\">\n      <div class=\"cal-date\">教练评价</div>\n      <div><div class=\"cal-desc\">主教练Jon Scheyer赞扬球队在下半场的防守表现和团队应变能力，特别表扬了Maliq Brown的无私精神和竞争意识</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <a href=\"https://dukechronicle.com/article/duke-mens-basketball-north-carolina-game-recap-scheyer-boozer-evans-brown-ngongba-foster-sarr-wilson-veesar-trimble-20260308\" target=\"_blank\">原文链接（Duke Chronicle）</a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
    "created_at": "2026-03-08T14:54:28.394116+00:00"
  },
  {
    "id": "8be3d6cd-7257-431f-a2ad-d5b8642faf06",
    "title": "TWICE AS NICE: Duke women's basketball outlasts Louisville 70-65 in overtime for 2nd-straight ACC title",
    "date": "3/8/2026",
    "html": "<div class=\"sub-accordion\">\n  <button class=\"sub-accordion-btn\" onclick=\"toggleSubAccordion(this)\">\n    <span>杜克女篮连续第二年夺得ACC锦标赛冠军<span class=\"tag tag-key\">2026.3.8</span></span>\n    <span class=\"sub-accordion-arrow\">&#9658;</span>\n  </button>\n  <div class=\"sub-accordion-body\">\n    <div class=\"cal-highlight\">\n      <strong>历史性胜利：连续两年ACC冠军</strong><br>\n      杜克大学女子篮球队在加时赛中以70-65击败路易斯维尔大学，获得连续第二个ACC锦标赛冠军。这是自2010-2011年以来首次实现背靠背夺冠，展现了杜克体育项目的卓越实力。\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cal-item\">\n      <div class=\"cal-date\">比赛亮点</div>\n      <div><div class=\"cal-desc\">在常规时间最后4.6秒追平比分，加时赛关键时刻表现出色，Thomas和Mair各贡献19分</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cal-item\">\n      <div class=\"cal-date\">教练评价</div>\n      <div><div class=\"cal-desc\">主教练Kara Lawson赞扬球队在关键时刻保持稳定，称赞球员们都是\"胜利者\"</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cal-item\">\n      <div class=\"cal-date\">下一步</div>\n      <div><div class=\"cal-desc\">球队将等待3月15日公布的NCAA锦标赛种子排名，有望在全国大赛中继续创造佳绩</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <a href=\"https://dukechronicle.com/article/duke-womens-basketball-acc-championship-louisville-game-recap-lawson-fournier-mair-jackson-roberson-nelson-thomas-wood-berry-randolph-roberts-20260308\" target=\"_blank\">原文链接（Duke Chronicle）</a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
    "created_at": "2026-03-08T23:20:31.977007+00:00"
  },
  {
    "id": "aec87693-b1b4-4d9c-8064-fcec8233932d",
    "title": "Duke undergraduate cost of attendance to exceed $96,000 in 2026-27",
    "date": "3/10/26",
    "html": "<div class=\"sub-accordion\">\n  <button class=\"sub-accordion-btn\" onclick=\"toggleSubAccordion(this)\">\n    <span>杜克大学2026-27学年费用将超过9.6万美元<span class=\"tag tag-fall\">2026.3.10</span></span>\n    <span class=\"sub-accordion-arrow\">&#9658;</span>\n  </button>\n  <div class=\"sub-accordion-body\">\n    <div class=\"cal-highlight\">\n      <strong>学费大幅上涨预警</strong><br>\n      杜克大学宣布2026-27学年本科生总费用将达到96,597美元，较今年上涨4.95%。这是连续第二年大幅涨价，远超过去十年平均涨幅。\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cal-item\">\n      <div class=\"cal-date\">费用构成</div>\n      <div><div class=\"cal-desc\">学费73,740美元，住宿费及其他费用22,857美元，总计96,597美元</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cal-item\">\n      <div class=\"cal-date\">四年总成本</div>\n      <div><div class=\"cal-desc\">2027届学生四年总费用将超过35.8万美元，较入学时上涨16%</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cal-item\">\n      <div class=\"cal-date\">财政援助</div>\n      <div><div class=\"cal-desc\">约一半学生获得经济援助，超过20%学生免学费入学，援助金额会随学费调整</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <a href=\"https://dukechronicle.com/article/duke-university-announces-undergraduate-cost-of-attendance-for-2025-2026-academic-year-tuition-room-board-20260310\" target=\"_blank\">原文链接（Duke Chronicle）</a>\n  </div>\n</div>",
    "created_at": "2026-03-10T20:22:51.768596+00:00"
  }
]